<item>
            <title>[LU-5845] need new spec file and build changes for e2fsprogs build on SLES 12</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5845</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In order to do production builds of our e2fsprogs on SLES12 we will need a mod something like &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/11147&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/11147&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5307&quot; title=&quot;e2fsprogs build fails in Centos 7&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5307&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5307&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; build: add support for RHEL-7 .spec file.  That previous mod adds build support for el7.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the absence of such a mod I have temporally been building e2fsprogs on SLES 12 using the existing SLES 11 spec file, slightly edited.  That seems to work OK.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>SLES 12</environment>
        <key id="25820">LU-5845</key>
