                            <comment id="98330" author="bogl" created="Tue, 4 Nov 2014 20:16:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;fix landed in master-lustre branch of tools/e2fsprogs&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="98176" author="bogl" created="Mon, 3 Nov 2014 14:50:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;now that SLES 12 has been announced this ticket may be public&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="96664" author="bogl" created="Sun, 19 Oct 2014 18:57:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;As commented in &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/12316&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/12316&lt;/a&gt; can&apos;t become LU until sles12 is announced, or at least made public.   Just noticed that release notes dated 10/10 are now published on the SuSE website.  Don&apos;t know if that is public enough to let us talk about it in public Jira tickets or not.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="96639" author="adilger" created="Fri, 17 Oct 2014 21:19:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Can this bug be moved to the LU space, so that the patch can be landed?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="96515" author="bogl" created="Thu, 16 Oct 2014 18:49:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/12316&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/12316&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="90672" author="bogl" created="Sun, 3 Aug 2014 00:27:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The spec file I posted here is now a bit out of date.  The native e2fsprogs in the latest SLES12 release, SLES 12 RC1, is now 1.42.11-1.2.  If the .spec file from 1.42.9 I attached isn&apos;t good enough please let me know.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="90590" author="bogl" created="Thu, 31 Jul 2014 20:13:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;.spec file from native SLES 12 rpm e2fsprogs-1.42.9-2.10.src.rpm&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
